des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in Philly.. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Philly Vegan." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Philly Vegan for a fact."
